---
title: Indian Coconut Beef Curry with Garlic Rice & Toasted Almonds
description: This creamy coconut beef curry will add the spice you never knew you needed to your night. It's filled to the brim with bright veggies and finished with a sprinkling of flair from the toasted almonds.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/indian-coconut-beef-curry-5a4207af.jpg
